1. *Legenda* kaže da je ovaj grad osnovan pre više od hiljadu godina. (The *legend* says that this city was founded more than a thousand years ago.)
2. Proslavljeni košarkaš smatra se *legendom* u svojoj zemlji. (The celebrated basketball player is considered a *legend* in his country.)
3. Ovaj restoran je *legenda* među gurmanima. (This restaurant is a *legend* among foodies.)
4. Širila se *legenda* da je kuća ukleta. (There was a *legend* that the house was cursed.)
5. Naše bake su *legende* kada je u pitanju priprema tradicionalnih jela. (Our grandmothers are *legends* when it comes to preparing traditional dishes.)
6. Novinarska *legenda* izvestila je o ratu u mnogim zemljama širom sveta. (The journalistic *legend* reported on the war in many countries around the world.)
7. Zlatna *legenda* srpskog fudbala, Dragan Džajić, je nedavno dobio orden za životno delo. (The golden *legend* of Serbian football, Dragan Džajić, recently received a lifetime achievement award.)
8. Postoji *legenda* o tajanstvenom blagu koje je skriveno negde u ovom kraju. (There is a *legend* about a mysterious treasure that is hidden somewhere in this region.)
9. U filmu igraju dve glumačke *legende* - Džek Nikolson i Meryl Strip. (Two acting *legends* - Jack Nicholson and Meryl Streep - star in the movie.)
10. Na današnji dan se sećamo *legende* koja je ostavila neizbrisiv trag u istoriji srpske književnosti. (On this day, we remember a *legend* who left an indelible mark on the history of Serbian literature.)